detail.paragraph3:
Bua kutambula bimpe bwa bulongolodi, Conseil d'État ebenza ne:
1. Bifukama bibidi;
2. Dibunge dia bantu bonso;
3. Biro;
4. Misambu ya bulongolodi ne ya teknik.

<strong>Bifukama bia Conseil d'État</strong>

Conseil d'État ebinene ne bifukama bia kusambilila ne bia kulongolola makambo.
Bifukama bionso bibi ne tshisumbu tshimo to mingi.
